<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">远程登录您的设备</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">您可以使用远程桌面连接应用程序从另一台设备登录您的用户账号。配置<span class="gui">远程登录</span>以访问您的设备并设置安全首选项。</p>
<p class="p">如果您想让其他人查看或控制您的桌面，请参阅<span class="link"><a href="sharing-desktop.html.zh-CN" title="共享您的桌面">桌面共享</a></span>。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">系统</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">从结果中选择<span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">设置</span> ▸ <span class="gui">系统</span></span>。这将打开<span class="gui">系统</span>面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">选择 <span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">远程桌面</span> ▸ <span class="gui">远程登录</span></span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">解锁</span>并认证以修改设置。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">要远程登录您的用户账号，请打开<span class="gui">远程登录</span>。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div>
<section id="connecting"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">连接</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p"><span class="gui">如何连接</span> 部分显示可在连接设备上使用的 <span class="gui">主机名</span> 和 <span class="gui">端口</span>。如果要将其放置在剪贴板中，请点击每个条目旁边的按钮。也可以使用<span class="link"><a href="net-findip.html.zh-CN" title="查看您的 IP 地址">IP 地址</a></span>建立连接。</p>
<div class="note note-important" title="重要">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m12.5 2a9.5 9.5 0 0 0-9.5 9.5 9.5 9.5 0 0 0 9.5 9.5 9.5 9.5 0 0 0 9.5-9.5 9.5 9.5 0 0 0-9.5-9.5zm0 3a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5 1.5v6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5zm0 10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5 1.5 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">如果开启了<span class="gui">远程登录</span>，它会将其端口号设置为 3389。如果您还使用<span class="link"><a href="sharing-desktop.html.zh-CN" title="共享您的桌面">桌面共享</a></span>，它会使用不同的端口号，例如 3390。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="authentication"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">认证</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p"><span class="gui">登录详情</span>显示您通过远程桌面客户端软件连接到您的用户账号时需要输入的用户名和密码。</p>
<div class="note note-tip" title="提示">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m12 2c-3.8541 0-7 3.1459-7 7 0 1.823 0.4945 3.139 1.1641 4.133 0.6695 0.994 1.4328 1.671 2.039 2.471 0.0882 0.116 0.1749 0.656 0.2071 1.32 0.016 0.332 0.0133 0.68 0.1894 1.119 0.0881 0.22 0.2439 0.478 0.5059 0.672 0.2619 0.194 0.6028 0.285 0.8945 0.285h4c0.583 0 1.204-0.478 1.402-0.908 0.199-0.43 0.217-0.793 0.244-1.137 0.056-0.688 0.138-1.319 0.211-1.441 0.549-0.916 1.304-2.009 1.94-3.114 0.636-1.104 1.203-2.199 1.203-3.4 0-3.8541-3.146-7-7-7zm0 2c2.773 0 5 2.2267 5 5 0 0.456-0.359 1.401-0.936 2.402-0.111 0.195-0.246 0.399-0.369 0.598h-7.8825c-0.4871-0.728-0.8125-1.519-0.8125-3 0-2.7733 2.2267-5 5-5z" style="block-progression:tb;color-rendering:auto;color:#000000;image-rendering:auto;isolation:auto;mix-blend-mode:normal;shape-rendering:auto;solid-color:#000000;text-decoration-color:#000000;text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration-style:solid;text-indent:0;text-transform:none;white-space:normal"></path>
